            <title>[OAK-1827] ClassCastException in NodeDocument.split() when collisions detected</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-1827</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When writing nodes concurrently, collisions are detected and the following warnings are logged:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;18:49:33.202 [DocumentNodeStore background thread] WARN  o.a.j.o.p.document.DocumentNodeStore - Background operation failed: java.lang.ClassCastException: java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Boolean&lt;/span&gt; cannot be &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;cast&lt;/span&gt; to java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;
java.lang.ClassCastException: java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Boolean&lt;/span&gt; cannot be &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;cast&lt;/span&gt; to java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.document.NodeDocument.split(NodeDocument.java:919) ~[classes/:na]
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.document.DocumentNodeStore.backgroundSplit(DocumentNodeStore.java:1461) ~[classes/:na]
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.document.DocumentNodeStore.runBackgroundOperations(DocumentNodeStore.java:1370) ~[classes/:na]
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.document.DocumentNodeStore$BackgroundOperation.execute(DocumentNodeStore.java:1755) ~[classes/:na]
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.document.DocumentNodeStore$NodeStoreTask.run(DocumentNodeStore.java:1730) ~[classes/:na]
	at java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Thread&lt;/span&gt;.run(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Thread&lt;/span&gt;.java:662) [na:1.6.0_41]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
